The girl gets a job as a secretary. During the interview, the boss explained his job responsibilities and asks:
- And so, is everything clear to you, if you have any questions, ask.
The girl asks:
- Everything is clear in principle, but what will be the salary?
The boss:
- Two hundred dollars.
Girl:
- Of course it's not enough.
The boss:
- Well, with a stretch, maybe two hundred and fifty.
The girl clarifies:
- Excuse me, but will it be just you or your deputy who will pull it on?
